  <div class="hero-image-full fade-in">
    <img src="/images/camden-window-film-company.jpg" alt="Window film installation Camden NJ" width="1200" height="380" loading="lazy" />
    <span class="hero-image-caption">📍 Serving all Camden neighborhoods & surrounding areas</span>
