<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     MAIN CONTENT + SIDEBAR
     ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="content-wrap">
  <div class="main-content prose">
    <h2>Camden's Trusted Window Film Experts</h2>
    <p>At Window Film Philadelphia, we've been serving Camden and the surrounding South Jersey communities since 2008. Whether you're looking to reduce the summer heat in your home, improve energy efficiency in your office, protect your storefront from graffiti, or add decorative privacy film to a conference room — our certified installers deliver flawless results every time.</p>
    <p>Camden's urban environment comes with unique challenges: high crime rates, intense summer humidity, and commercial properties that need maximum protection. Our window films are engineered to address every one of these concerns, providing security reinforcement, heat rejection, and UV blocking in a single installation.</p>

    <div class="callout">
      <p><strong>Camden Security Advantage:</strong> With a crime rate of 43.71 per 1,000 residents, Camden businesses and homeowners benefit greatly from security window film that holds glass together on impact, deters smash-and-grab theft, and protects occupants during severe weather events.</p>
    </div>

    <h2>Window Film Options for Camden Properties</h2>
    <p>We offer a curated selection of premium films from 3M, LLumar, Vista, and Solar Gard — matched to Camden's specific urban climate and your project goals.</p>

    <div class="film-grid">
      <div class="film-card featured">
        <span class="film-badge">Most Popular</span>
        <h4>Solar Control Film</h4>
        <p>Maximum heat rejection and UV blocking. Ideal for Camden homes and offices facing south or west exposures.</p>
        <div class="film-price">From $6.50/sq ft installed</div>
      </div>
      <div class="film-card">
        <h4>Safety & Security Film</h4>
        <p>Holds glass together on impact. Popular for commercial storefronts, ground-floor offices, and residential ground floors.</p>
        <div class="film-price">From $7.00/sq ft installed</div>
      </div>
      <div class="film-card">
        <h4>Decorative & Privacy Film</h4>
        <p>Frosted, patterned, or custom-cut designs for bathrooms, conference rooms, and storefronts.</p>
        <div class="film-price">From $5.50/sq ft installed</div>
      </div>
      <div class="film-card">
        <h4>Anti-Graffiti Film</h4>
        <p>Sacrificial film layer protects glass from etching, paint, and graffiti damage. Easily replaced at low cost.</p>
        <div class="film-price">From $4.00/sq ft installed</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2>Why Camden Properties Choose Window Film Philadelphia</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>15+ years serving the Philadelphia and South Jersey area</li>
      <li>Factory-certified installation technicians from 3M, LLumar, and Vista</li>
      <li>Manufacturer-backed lifetime warranty on all residential and commercial films</li>
      <li>Same-week appointments available across Camden County</li>
      <li>Free in-home and on-site consultations</li>
      <li>Philadelphia's most reviewed window film contractor</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Our Camden Installation Process</h2>
    <p>We keep it simple. Call or submit a quote request and receive a detailed estimate within 24 hours. Our Camden-area crew arrives on schedule, preps the surface, installs the film, and leaves your space spotless. Most residential jobs are completed in a single day.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="sidebar-wrap">
    <div class="sidebar-card fade-in">
      <h4>Recent Camden Reviews</h4>
      <div class="review-mini">
        <div class="review-avatar">SR</div>
        <div>
          <div class="review-name">Sarah R. — Cramer Hill</div>
          <div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <div class="review-text">"Incredible difference in our living room. Professional team, on time, and spotless cleanup."</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-mini">
        <div class="review-avatar">DM</div>
        <div>
          <div class="review-name">Dave M. — Camden Storefront</div>
          <div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <div class="review-text">"Security film on our storefront glass gives us real peace of mind. The AC bill dropped noticeably too."</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-mini">
        <div class="review-avatar">KL</div>
        <div>
          <div class="review-name">Kat L. — Fairview</div>
          <div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <div class="review-text">"Best window film job we've had. Cool, private, and the decorative film looks amazing."</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="sidebar-card fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
      <h4>Certifications & Partners</h4>
      <div class="badge-row">
        <div class="cert-badge">🏅 3M Certified</div>
        <div class="cert-badge">✓ LLumar Dealer</div>
        <div class="cert-badge">🛡️ Vista Film</div>
        <div class="cert-badge">⭐ BBB A+</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="sidebar-card fade-in fade-in-delay-2">
      <h4>Camden Service Area</h4>
      <p class="sidebar-area-note">We serve all Camden neighborhoods and surrounding South Jersey suburbs, typically within 1–2 business days.</p>
      <div class="neighborhood-tags">
        <span class="tag">Cramer Hill</span>
        <span class="tag">Fairview</span>
        <span class="tag">Waterfront South</span>
        <span class="tag">Parkside</span>
        <span class="tag">Woodlynne</span>
        <span class="tag">Cherry Hill</span>
        <span class="tag">Haddonfield</span>
        <span class="tag">Collingswood</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

