      <div class="neighborhood-tags">
        <span class="tag">Camden</span>
        <span class="tag">Cherry Hill</span>
        <span class="tag">Haddonfield</span>
        <span class="tag">Collingswood</span>
        <span class="tag">Pennsauken</span>
        <span class="tag">Merchantville</span>
        <span class="tag">Maple Shade</span>
        <span class="tag">Voorhees</span>
        <span class="tag">+ more</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     FAQ ACCORDION
     ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="faq-section">
  <div class="faq-header">
    <p class="section-eyebrow">FAQ</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Common questions about Camden window film</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item open">
    <div class="faq-q">Is window film legal in New Jersey? <span class="faq-toggle">+</span></div>
    <div class="faq-a">Yes. New Jersey law permits residential and commercial window film without restriction. For automotive applications, NJ requires front side windows to allow at least 35% visible light transmission. We ensure all installs are fully compliant.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <div class="faq-q">How long does installation take? <span class="faq-toggle">+</span></div>
    <div class="faq-a">Most residential jobs take 4–8 hours. Commercial projects are scoped per job. Anti-graffiti and decorative films can often be completed in a single afternoon.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <div class="faq-q">What warranty comes with my installation? <span class="faq-toggle">+</span></div>
    <div class="faq-a">All our residential and commercial installations include a lifetime manufacturer warranty against peeling, bubbling, and fading. The warranty travels with the property, not the owner.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <div class="faq-q">How much does window film cost in Camden? <span class="faq-toggle">+</span></div>
    <div class="faq-a">Residential solar control film starts around $5–$8 per square foot installed. Security film starts at $7/sq ft. Anti-graffiti starts at $4/sq ft. Request a free quote for an exact estimate based on your property.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <div class="faq-q">Do you offer free consultations in Camden? <span class="faq-toggle">+</span></div>
    <div class="faq-a">Yes — all consultations are free. We'll come to your home or business, assess your needs, and provide a detailed written estimate at no charge and no obligation.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <div class="faq-q">How soon can you schedule in Camden? <span class="faq-toggle">+</span></div>
    <div class="faq-a">We typically have same-week availability in the Camden area. During peak summer months we recommend booking 1–2 weeks in advance.</div>
  </div>
</div>

